":"","fullscreen":{},"gif":{},"bgc":"issue"}{"image":"assets/images/issues/2018/20/punkt-widokowy/dziedzictwo/13.jpg","image_caption":"","fullscreen":{"0":"1"},"gif":{},"bgc":"black"}{"image":"assets/images/issues/2018/20/punkt-widokowy/dziedzictwo/14.jpg","image_caption":"","fullscreen":{},"gif":{},"bgc":"black"}{"image":"assets/images/issues/2018/20/punkt-widokowy/dziedzictwo/15.jpg","image_caption":"","fullscreen":{"0":"1"},"gif":{},"bgc":"black"}{"image":"assets/images/issues/2018/20/punkt-widokowy/dziedzictwo/16.jpg","image_caption":"","fullscreen":{},"gif":{},"bgc":"white"}{"image":"assets/images/issues/2018/20/punkt-widokowy/dziedzictwo/17.jpg","image_caption":"","fullscreen":{"0":"1"},"gif":{},"bgc":"black"}{"image":"assets/images/issues/2018/20/punkt-widokowy/dziedzictwo/18.jpg","image_caption":"","fullscreen":{},"gif":{},"bgc":"issue"}{"image":"assets/images/issues/2018/20/punkt-widokowy/dziedzictwo/19.jpg","image_caption":"","fullscreen":{"0":"1"},"gif":{},"bgc":"black"}{"content":"<p>The seventh edition of the queer festival Pomada titled “Sex, Lies, and Videotapes,” as well as the main festival exhibition titled “Heritage,” took place between September 29 and October 1, 2017.</p>\n<p>The festival was organized by: Michał Grzegorzek, Aleksandra Knychalska, Joanna Manecka, Karol Radziszewski, and Justyna Sobolak.</p>\n<p>Michał Grzegorzek, Karol Radziszewski and Wojciech Szymański curated the “Heritage” exhibition, which took place in the Czesław Miłosz room of the Palace of Culture and Science in Warsaw.</p>\n<p>Photographs: Bartek Górka.</p>","bgc":"black"}";s:8:"richtext";s:1:"1";s:8:"template";s:2:"43";s:9:"menuindex";s:1:"1";s:10:"searchable";s:1:"1";s:9:"cacheable";s:1:"1";s:9:"createdby";s:2:"11";s:9:"createdon";s:10:"1551732951";s:8:"editedby";s:2:"11";s:8:"editedon";s:10:"1557451918";s:7:"deleted";s:1:"0";s:9:"deletedon";s:1:"0";s:9:"deletedby";s:1:"0";s:11:"publishedon";s:10:"1551733504";s:11:"publishedby";s:2:"11";s:9:"menutitle";s:0:"";s:7:"do